title: Donald Trump Warns That Syrian Refugees May Be A ‘Trojan Horse’ For ISIS, Calls Merkel ‘Insane’
text: The GOP presidential front runner and businessman Donald Trump is warning that Syrian refugees may be “the greatest Trojan horse” ever for the Islamic State terrorist group. Trump claims that ISIS could be placing its troops into various countries under the guise that they are Syrian refugees. Therefore, he says that German Chancellor Angela Merkel...
